<br>
To my amazement, I heard and then saw confirmed that druids now have armor dropping in Hate. It is just so patently obvious how much Verant love playing their damned dr00ds.<br>
<br>
Hey more power to 'em I want other classes to be getting more breaks, but heck ... I have YET to see a piece of carmine drop in my Fear raids and watching all the melee and other classes walking away with fat lewt is just such a damn tease! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uqaman.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qaman</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/3/01 1:08:15 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Verant does it again!</span><hr size=1> Relax. The Druid/Ranger/Paladin drops in Hate are because they do not have any drops in the Plane of Growth, where we do have some decent drops.<br>
<br>
Never has been a lot of wizard drops in Hate. The Wand of Conflagaration is a random drop. Chests only dropped legs that I have ever seen. The new boss mobs can drops the Diamond Rod and Rod of Unbound Thought that Inny used to drop. And Eye of Innoruuk, but that usually goes to Necros although if they are nice you can use one til they need it (I have one). Few new things that are wiz usable include the Hate Crystal, Raiment of the Chosen, Mantle of Study, Abjurer's Earring, Crown of Hatred plus the new Inny drops. Usability of some of the stuff seems pretty low to me, and the High Elf drop off Inny kind of sucks. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugrimstafftheurgist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimstaff Theurgist</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www,kestrelarts.com/images/book.jpg BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/5/01 7:41:54 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Verant does it again!</span><hr size=1> One of the most amusing threads I ever saw was one started by Druids yet again bitching about how few quests they  have and how little equipment.<br>
<br>
So some guy went through EVERY database and listed all the quests and all the items specific to each class.  Guess who had fewer of each than Druids?  Yeah, you guessed it, Verant's whipping boy.  Druids shut up about the items and quests after that, you used to see them always bitching about it and now there's no complaints at all.<br>
<br>
It was funny and sad at the same time, but I did notice a lot of support behind Wizard threads after that.  That kind of thing more than anything is why they shut down the boards, in my opinion. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uabuzenwrathcaster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Abuzen Wrathcaster</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/6/01 6:03:09 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Verant does it again!</span><hr size=1> Yeah, I was thinking about Wizard Quests last night, and I realized...  All of the other classes have quest pieces that you can hand to them.  Wizard stuff is all No Drop.  I mean EVERYTHING is No Drop!  Tishan's Kilt, Acumen Mask, Staff of Temperate Flux, Runescale Cloak...  Then I think about Crafted and Etched Ivy, and I wanna vomit.<br>
<br>
Verant doesn't even make an attempt to hide how biased they are against Int Casters. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=aennyilofkarana>Aennyil of Karana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/8/01 8:23:13 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Verant does it again!</span><hr size=1> Thanks Oaman, now I can feel bad that I've never seen a wiz item drop in any of the planar raids I've been on even though there was a chance for it, lol.<br>
<br>
As for PoG, can you please explain to me what I can do to fix my faction hits after I go hunt there? Bad enough the druids at the ring in NK wanna rape me for killing treants, hehe. I would like to be able to go back to Felwithe to shop :-) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=yiliamar>Yiliamar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/8/01 8:34:00 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Verant does it again!</span><hr size=1> Go to Erudin, Aennyil.  Nicer city. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uerithe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Erithe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/11/01 11:12:31 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Verant does it again!</span><hr size=1> I can't kill on PoG ... Tunare Deity choice was made before I ever had actually played the game  and understood what it meant.  Wish there were quests to change deities. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showMessage?topicID=124.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showMessage?topicID=110.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.emailToFriend?topicID=109.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.threadControl?topicID=109.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=109.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=109.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSFo